ph|last11=Phue|first11=Je Nie|last12=Wright|first12=Linda L.|last13=Muyembe-Tamfum|first13=Jean-Jacques|last14=Sullivan|first14=Nancy J.|last15=Rimoin|first15=Anne W.|title=Serologic Evidence of Ebolavirus Infection in a Population With No History of Outbreaks in the Democratic Republic of the Congo|journal=The Journal of Infectious Diseases|volume=217|issue=4|pages=529\u2013537|date=10 January 2018|doi=10.1093/infdis/jix619|pmid=29329455|pmc=5853806|issn=1537-6613}}\n* {{cite journal|title=The role of training in the West Africa Ebola response World Health Organization A review of the role of training in WHO Ebola emergency response|journal=Weekly Epidemiological Record|date=April 2016|format=PDF|url=http://www.who.int/wer/2016/wer9114.pdf?ua=1|accessdate=24 April 2016}}\n*{{cite journal |display-authors=3 |last1=Dickson|first1=S. J.|last2=Clay|first2=K. A.|last3=Adam|first3=M.|last4=Ardley|first4=C.|last5=Bailey|first5=M. S.|last6=Burns|first6=D. S.|last7=Cox|first7=A. T.|last8=Craig|first8=D. G.|last9=Espina|first9=M.|last10=Fitchett|first10=G.|last11=Grindrod|first11=J.|last12=Hinsley|first12=D. E.|last13=Horne|first13=S.|last14=Hutley|first14=E.|last15=Johnston|first15=A. M.|last16=Kao|first16=R. L. C.|last17=Lamb|first17=L. E.|last18=Lewis|first18=S.|last19=Marion|first19=D.|last20=Moore|first20=A. J.|last21=Nicholson-Roberts|first21=T. C.|last22=Phillips|first22=A.|last23=Praught|first23=J.|last24=Rees|first24=P. S.|last25=Schoonbaert|first25=I.|last26=Trinick|first26=T.|last27=Wilson|first27=D. R.|last28=Simpson|first28=A. J.|last29=Wang|first29=D.|last30=O'Shea|first30=M. K.|last31=Fletcher|first31=T. E.|last32=Ewington|first32=I.|title=Enhanced case management can be delivered for patients with EVD in Africa: Experience from a UK military Ebola treatment centre in Sierra Leone|journal=The Journal of Infection|volume=76|issue=4|pages=383\u2013392|date=14 December 2017|doi=10.1016/j.jinf.2017.12.006|pmid=29248587|pmc=5903873|issn=1532-2742}}\n*{{cite journal